Package: CaveDive
Title: Phylodynamics for Clonal Expansion
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("David", "Helekal", email = "David.Helekal@warwick.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: CaveDive implements simulations and inference of phylogenies containing phylodynamic signatures consistent with the presence of one or several clonal expansions within the sampled population.
